CycleSync Privacy Policy

Introduction

Welcome to CycleSync ("we," "our," or "us"). Your privacy is critically important to us, especially given the sensitive nature of menstrual and health data. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our Chrome extension.

Information We Collect
Personal Information
* Menstrual cycle data: Period start and end dates, cycle length
* Symptom information: Physical and emotional symptoms logged by you
* User preferences: Settings and customizations within the extension
How Information Is Collected
* Direct input: Information you voluntarily enter when using the extension
* Automatic collection: Usage statistics to improve the extension functionality
* Local storage: All your data is stored locally on your device using Chrome's storage API

How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:
* Provide cycle tracking and predictions
* Offer personalized insights and recommendations
* Improve the extension's functionality and user experience

Data Storage and Security
Local Storage
All your personal data is stored locally on your device using Chrome's storage API. Your sensitive health information does not leave your browser unless you explicitly choose to export it.
Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect against unauthorized access to or unauthorized alteration, disclosure, or destruction of data. These measures include internal reviews of our data collection, storage, and processing practices and security measures.
Data Sharing

We Do Not Share Your Data
* We do not send your personal data to our servers
* We do not share your information with third parties
* We do not use your data for advertising purposes
Optional Integration Services

If you choose to enable optional features such as calendar integration, minimal necessary data may be shared with those services according to your explicit permission.
Your Choices and Rights
You have the ability to:
* Access all your data directly within the extension
* Export your data in a portable format
* Delete your data at any time through the Settings menu
* Control notifications and reminders

Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy in the extension and updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at: wushumaster75@gmail.com

By using CycleSync, you consent to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
